---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)] bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-8 md:flex-row md:items-center">
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/logo.png" alt="sinunmango" width="32" height="32" class="h-8 w-8" />
          <span class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">sinunmango</span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-soft)]">
          Una app argentina para llevar tus finanzas sin que te vuelva loco.
          Hecha por una persona, para personas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-2 text-sm sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]">
            Producto
          </p>
          <a href="#features" class="block text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)]">Qué hace</a>
          <a href="#pricing" class="block text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)]">Planes</a>
          <a href="#vistas" class="block text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)]">Vistas</a>
          <a href="https://app.sinunmango.com.ar" class="block text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)]">Ir a la app</a>
          <a
            href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sinunmango.mobile"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="block text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)]"
          >Google Play</a>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]">
            Soporte
          </p>
          <a href="#faq" class="block text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)]">Preguntas</a>
          <a href="mailto:luchobessan@gmail.com" class="block text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)]">Contacto</a>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-ink-muted)]">
            Legal
          </p>
          <a href="/privacidad" class="block text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)]">Privacidad</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-3 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] pt-6 text-xs text-[var(--color-ink-muted)] sm:flex-row sm:items-center"
    >
      <p>© {year} sinunmango. Hecho en Buenos Aires, con mate.</p>
      <p>
        sinunmango no es un banco ni un asesor financiero. Es una herramienta
        para que sepas dónde está tu plata.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
